description:
Sniper 1945: World War II is drawing to a close and the Soviets and Nazi's are caught in a furious battle for Berlin. Taking the role of an American Sniper sent into the chaos of war-torn Berlin by the Secret Service, the player must complete a series of vitally important missions to thwart Soviet nuclear ambitions at the dawn of the Cold War.

Features 

Features a combination of 3rd and 1st person gameplay.
Non-linear hostile environments.
Sophisticated enemy AI and mission design.
Single-player Berlin campaign consists of 28 missions, complemented by a two-player co-op mode and online multiplayer modes.*



